.jpg&h=8dcc6da8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n途中有人插隊互屌 不過啲警察保安都唔理嘅 話之佢地嘈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XN8Fnkn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXN8Fnkn.jpg&h=fe26f60d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住就搵淘寶個老板比我呢個大陸電話佢 等個導遊聯絡到我join d local tour<br />\n<br />\n 唔知火車有咩食物賣 買左兩個包一支水預防萬一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ctmWE77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FctmWE77.jpg&h=85fc96e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家就等緊上火車！<br />\n用面具巴打推薦嘅VPN master <br />\n上到所有網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WW5o4Am.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWW5o4Am.jpg&h=cf38472a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vyJ4Ap.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vyJ4Ap.jpg&h=c38af2ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNQMhVK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNQMhVK.jpg&h=719414a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咁多先 無咩電 唔知火車有無插位比人叉電呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ee4e741c776c82842d7c128bd09c8fd4fe259b","tid":1115063,"uid":33878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:13:09.000Z","msg":"上左火車<br />\n無位叉電<br />\n我訓中層<br />\n樓下一對母子<br />\n樓上一個西裝人<br />\n隔離床有個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n套衫OK 不過唔靚嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢坐左係到食薯片唔敢影 無圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DX7KPh5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDX7KPh5.jpg&h=587891e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/19/170734_edcf4cdda93da81fe74337b70295a687.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F19%2F170734_edcf4cdda93da81fe74337b70295a687.jpg&h=c42be9e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q2EX9iz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq2EX9iz.jpg&h=76f0515b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/19/170614_df1b787bed04702fcaddca3351b03e89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F19%2F170614_df1b787bed04702fcaddca3351b03e89.jpg&h=56f6a7e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說啱啱係羅湖過關有個姨姨屌柒個支那入境制服人員唔比佢同佢個仔排一條隊 屌到成個大堂都聽到 幾夠guts 直到個大陸佬話警告要拘留佢 佢至收火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4df1d5514b31b7899ef82f9d710d19a0fd8973","tid":1115063,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:50:31.000Z","msg":"樓下個媽媽同佢個寶寶講故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c97432b70aceb5ba43b26d896719dadeb6f2c50","tid":1115063,"uid":33878,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T22:32:40.000Z","msg":"上到火車 廁所比想象中乾淨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oCJYYcy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoCJYYcy.jpg&h=c5e7540a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wqzYdLQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwqzYdLQ.jpg&h=09d62529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五點落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住求其係車站外食左碗鹵肉粉 八蚊<br />\n等十點司機黎搵我join tour<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sta8A0h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSta8A0h.jpg&h=0980d1f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h5ORyMT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh5ORyMT.jpg&h=66a480a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AzqwyMQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAzqwyMQ.jpg&h=dd588b4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64fcc68620bad162bc6ffb733c1cb0529e06a0bf","tid":1115063,"uid":3619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:04:02.000Z","msg":"樓主呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47631638c12ebba15637a4b4d6a7a53f6311fc8","tid":1115063,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"64fcc68620bad162bc6ffb733c1cb0529e06a0bf","tid":1115063,"uid":3619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:04:02.000Z","msg":"樓主呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T04:35:53.000Z","msg":"無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />疏 <br />\n遲啲補翻"},{"pid":"ae3bc474c5f6cb4fe17a1a1b406a08f6dc9d768f","tid":1115063,"uid":3619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a47631638c12ebba15637a4b4d6a7a53f6311fc8","tid":1115063,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"64fcc68620bad162bc6ffb733c1cb0529e06a0bf","tid":1115063,"uid":3619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:04:02.000Z","msg":"樓主呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T04:35:53.000Z","msg":"無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />疏 <br />\n遲啲補翻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T09:07:22.000Z","msg":"我睇阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等你 唔好走數"},{"pid":"3268e4ccb11f727f8ac7ba873218adb2354b79a5","tid":1115063,"uid":33878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"黎到個司機係替更 唔係原本尋日約我個個 不過是撚但啦 都係男人一個 仲諗住會有靚女導遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢話佢今朝至頂原本個仆街 乜都係臨時臨急 佢係桂林當地人 佢自己都有接下旅行團 不過只限包車團 佢係咁話可以加佢wechat 毒撚我開頭無諗住加 諗住聽完就算 feel到佢其實想我加 就即刻拎wechat岀黎加下啦屌 廢事embarrassed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講野個時我成日噴左啲口水係佢成手到 佢扮無野抹係件衫到就算 我就扮唔知 既刻收下把口唔敢講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日計劃行程係會join tour跟司機由桂林搭六十分鐘竹筏遊漓江<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後去興坪古鎮行下食午飯<br />\n再去銀子岩睇洞穴啲岩石<br />\n然後搭車返陽朔～<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實佢黎到桂林北站停車場門口接我都九點十<br />\n之後去左四間酒店接左四班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一班人係深圳廣州黎嘅一女二男<br />\n唔知咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 二十幾歲 似男女朋友又似親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個女個樣ok 重點係心口幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個兩個鄉下男仔今晩就爽啦&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n這些機會 身為毒撚只可以間唔中偷望下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二組人係一對三十幾人嘅夫婦 大陸人 但係著衫唔Leung 講野文質彬彬 似一線城市啲人<br />\n第三組人 車去到holiday inn門口 睇見個名就覺得係香港人外國人住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住有一男一女嘅出黎 男嘅四五十 背囊插住個腳架 女嘅就港女三四十歲ol樣 我碌大對眼望住佢地 佢地都有少少驚訝咁望左我一下 然後上呢架七人車 我心諗佢地衣著腳架酒店都好香港人下<br />\n到佢地同導遊講野個下發現原來真係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\njoin taobao local tour得八條友都係桂林撞到香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n齊人開車個下 司機話由於近日桂林連場大雨 漓江水位上漲 所以今日無60分鐘竹筏坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只可以直接坐車去興坪古鎮搭大船岀漓江遊下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我即刻屌你老母 不過無計 政府規定 天氣問題 屌佢都無用&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;天有不測之風雲<br />\n我地成團人唯有接受直接搭兩個半鐘車去興坪&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n我嘅竹筏&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nbtw桂林市都幾多車多人多燈<br />\n載完全部人上車都成十一點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要搭兩粒半鐘車 全車人又無咩人岀聲 屌你老母 司機都唔岀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又搭通宵車朝早五點等到十點<br />\n開始有啲眼訓 醒下影下相訓到去興坪算～<br />\n途中發現有單車徑 其實如果得閒可以由桂林沿住漓江踩到陽朔 問過司機 佢話大半日應該得 <br />\n有國際單車比賽都係踩呢條線<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kN6wV1V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkN6wV1V.jpg&h=e334914c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPE22GU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPE22GU.jpg&h=dc4f5d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9UtWnGT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9UtWnGT.jpg&h=96e35e53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AJWwV1S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAJWwV1S.jpg&h=c7c9779a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y2c8dOw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy2c8dOw.jpg&h=c475444d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xum8Ye9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxum8Ye9.jpg&h=c67030bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0sk9HGO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0sk9HGO.jpg&h=3492a462&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4wivr8s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4wivr8s.jpg&h=c6a56a9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xVJWnGM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVJWnGM.jpg&h=6973eb00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41d0d54ac38977ce8eb8943a2c22f6de79b1bf09","tid":1115063,"uid":33878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T07:27:58.000Z","msg":"遲啲再打 打左成千幾字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一日上午完"},{"pid":"b43419fdf24c62d0311560d87368fc51514366cb","tid":1115063,"uid":46275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T07:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936d722a2ee151bee90d93d6e34c99d5660f601d","tid":1115063,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T07:54:24.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"e168b38683a4d1b43b659b7dcdeaa60f961e9014","tid":1115063,"uid":223916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T07:55:02.000Z","msg":"心口有幾大"},{"pid":"9eb4d1e65708b49a1b7f71d1e6cca588cfb8de49","tid":1115063,"uid":200937,"like":0,"dislike":